Associated members of Stichting IPA (Parents International) form 3 groups:&#xd;
a.	Individuals who have an affinity with the Foundation's objective and / or widen their knowledge about it;&#xd;
b.	Parents’ Associations registering at their own initiative or at the invitation of Stichting IPA&#xd;
c.	Organisations and other legal entities who work with/for parents but not parents’ associations.
